    "text": "# Ability Score Point Cost\n\nEach ability score costs a certain number of points.\n\n| Score | Cost |\n|-------|------|\n| 8     | 0    |\n| 9     | 1    |\n| 10    | 2    |\n| 11    | 3    |\n| 12    | 4    |\n| 13    | 5    |\n| 14    | 7    |\n| 15    | 9    |"
